{
 "file": "_STG18A.bin",
 "source_size": 40064,
 "built_size": 42375,
 "edits": [
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x11ca",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "十字先锋这个名号、我倒是有些耳闻",
   "zh_hex": "15ea4ae980ef8be967e7b9e828e8ace83302efcce848e7b6e7cbe8a4ee89ebac0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x11e2",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我记得、那应该是布霍·康采恩组建的私{00}人军队吧？",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce996e80a02e7b7e873e898e7b6e831ebfeef4beb57ec9ee7eeea0dea61e7b4efd500efb2e7e0e7c9e7d0050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x121c",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……是",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b60000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1223",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "十字先锋、是我的祖父麦兹亚·罗纳{00}他……",
   "zh_hex": "15ea4ae980b8e96702e7b68be7b4ebe1e888ec43e856e7d604e7ece88200e80c09090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x123c",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "为了建立宇宙巴比伦尼亚、而一手组建起{00}来的",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c1e7baea61e86be8bee8bfe85be825ea5be896e7d602e89c87aeea0dea61e84700d9e7b40000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x126e",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我听说、麦兹亚·罗纳是个贵族主义的忠{00}实信奉者",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce8d1e7ed02ec43e856e7d6ef4be7ece882e7b6e828e930eb5ee954e8cee7b4ec1800e87fe90feac1ef6e0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x128c",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这么说来、你们的思想、比起我们应该更{00}接近提坦斯和新吉翁才对",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7bde7edd902e7b8e7bbe7b4a6e7e602e825e8478be7bbe873e898e95200b796e821e843e7c8e7d3ef8ae7d9ee88e836e7be00000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x12ad",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那又是为何、要来协助我们呢？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e8f1e7b6e7c1efbc02ef2aefcfe8f6ea23efcce7bbe907050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x12d8",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "自从贝拉继承了祖父的事业、十字先锋就{00}已经变了",
   "zh_hex": "15efb5e88ae857e7c2e9d6ea75e7baebe1e888e7b4efb8eada02ea4ae980ef8be967e7c500ef3ae8b7e955e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1311",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……你是？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b8e7b6050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1334",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "金凯度·纳乌、海盗高达X1的驾驶员",
   "zh_hex": "15e902e95fe96def4be882e94d02e91be9f3e812ef2beed9eff7e7b4e953e975e8490000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1362",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "金凯度……你应该还有别的名字吧？",
   "zh_hex": "15e902e95fe96d0909e7b8e873e898e7f7e7cbe7e5e7b4e8ace980e7d0050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x139f",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "克瓦特罗·巴吉纳这名字、我看不怎么适{00}合你啊？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d5e99fe7cfe7ec04e85be7d9e882e7b9e8ace980028be7f6e7b5e7f2e7bdef4100a0e7b8e7c3050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x13de",
   "jp_len": 6,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1413",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "现在的我、就是金凯度·纳乌",
   "zh_hex": "15e82fef29e7b4efcc02e7c5e7b6e902e95fe96def4be882e94d0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1420",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "倒也不是说、我就仅仅是这么个身份而已{00}……",
   "zh_hex": "15e848e7c0e7b5e7b6e7ed02efcce7c5eb7aeb7ae7b6e7b9e7bde828e88dea22e89cef3a0009090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x143d",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "但至少、我决意要成为贝拉的力量、这一{00}点是事实",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dbe897b1028be8abef3cef2ae837e7c1e857e7c2e7b4dae85102e7b98700e822e7b6a9e87f00000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1456",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "贝拉的愿望、是打倒地球圈的敌人、并不{00}是为了散播贵族主义",
   "zh_hex": "15e857e7c2e7b4e961e96502e7b6e7f5e848ef63efd3e9fbe7b4e7e3efb202e957e7b500e7b6e7c1e7baef68ed70e930eb5ee954e8ce0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x147b",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唯独这一点、希望你们能相信",
   "zh_hex": "15ea89e8eee7b9efb6e82202e87be965e7b8e7bbe7c6e8b1e90f0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x14c7",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "嘛、要真是敌人、可不会特意帮我们把∀{00}给夺回来",
   "zh_hex": "15e93602ef2ae820e7b6e7e3efb202e7c4e7b5e7e2e7cfef3ce910efcce7bbe81beffe00e839ea17ef52efcf0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1509",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "要说是圈套、又未免做得太费工夫、不妨{00}就信他们一回吧？",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2ae7ede7b6e9fbeb3002e8f1e8b4eb7de81ce80ae86ae95deae4e83002e7b5e97f00e7c5e90fe80ce7bbefb6ef52e7d0050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1549",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……确实如此",
   "zh_hex": "150909e88ce87fe7f0e7ca0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1580",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么……你就是十字先锋的贝拉·罗纳、{00}对吧？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd0909e7b8e7c5e7b6ea4ae980ef8be967e7b4e857e7c2ef4be7ece8820200e7bee7d0050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x159b",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你们声称、是为了打倒敌人而行动的、可{00}是……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7bbea8aea0102e7b6e7c1e7bae7f5e848e7e3efb2e89cefd6ef30e7b402e7c400e7b609090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x15d7",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我们的敌人、目前尚未行动",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7bbe7b4e7e3efb202efd4ef51eccee8b4efd6ef300000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1604",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那敌人是？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7e3efb2e7b6050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x162b",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "现在还不能说、就算说了你们也不会信的",
   "zh_hex": "15e82fef29e7f7e7b5e7c6e7ed02e7c5e889e7ede7bae7b8e7bbe7c0e7b5e7e2e90fe7b40000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1661",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1683",
   "jp_len": 40,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "比起那些、我认为眼下当务之急、是与各{00}位协力、平定地球圈的混乱",
   "zh_hex": "15e825e847e7b7e8a4028be8a0e7c1e90b89c4e94fe7cdea6202e7b6e832e81900e834e8f6da02e887e867bf95e9fbe7b4ea41e9760000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x16c6",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "嗯……",
   "zh_hex": "15e86509090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x16cd",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "若真打退过金卡拉姆舰队、那对我们可是{00}求之不得的战力补充",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e7e820e7f5e880ef36e902e801e7c2e823e7d4e7c902e7b7e7beefcce7bbe7c4e7b600e93ae7cde7b5e80ae7b4ef28efb0ea81ea860000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x16f1",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我看不妨就答应下来、克瓦特罗大尉？",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7f6e7b5e97fe7c5ea96e873ef4defcf02e7d5e99fe7cfe7ecefa5efc6050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1722",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "说得也是……他们的力量、确实能助我们{00}一臂之力",
   "zh_hex": "15e7ede80ae7c0e7b60909e80ce7bbe7b4dae85102e88ce87fe7c6ea238be7bb0087ee92e7cdda000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1754",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么贝拉·罗纳……你们的这番提议、我{00}们就心怀感激地接受了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bde857e7c2ef4be7ece8820909e7b8e7bbe7b4e7b9ee6de821e8e302efcc00e7bbe7c5e82deb03e87de9b9ef63efcee8c8e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x178f",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……好的、今后还请多多关照",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7c7e7b402efb9e7fee7f7e83ae7e9e7e9e8bbea1a0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x17b5",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "用先锋母舰、来顶替离队的威尔盖姆吗{00}……",
   "zh_hex": "15d8b8e967e9d5e7d402d9eca1ea50e901e7c9e7b4e96be7e1ec7ee823e80200090900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x17cb",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "他们出现的这个时机、实在是再凑巧不过{00}了",
   "zh_hex": "15e80ce7bbefbee82fe7b4e7b9e828ef2de7e402e87fef29e7b6e80becb1ec13e7b5ef3600e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x17fb",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "今后还得面对提坦斯、新吉翁……",
   "zh_hex": "15a2e7fee7f7e80ae862e7bee821e843e7c802ef8ae7d9ee880909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x180b",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "再想到还得对付那个金卡拉姆、母舰不足{00}可就成了大问题",
   "zh_hex": "15e80be7e6e7d7e7f7e80ae7bee97ee7b7e828e902e801e7c2e82302e9d5e7d4e7b5ea1e00e7c4e7c5e837e7babee997ea12000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x182b",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "只不过、问题在于、我们该先从哪里下手{00}……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef32e7b5ef3602e997ea12ef29e87902efcce7bbe898ef8be88ae8ffef31ef4def660009090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x186e",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……什么！？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7dde7bdef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x189d",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "前方航路上有敌机！看这反应……是提坦{00}斯！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef51efb1e9c1e8d2ef4ce7cbe7e3e7e4ef97e7f6e7b9e87ce8730909e7b6e821e84300e7c8ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x18cf",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "用不着我们主动出击、他们倒自己送上门{00}来了！",
   "zh_hex": "15efb3e7b5e86defcce7bbe954ef30efbee7cc02e80ce7bbe848efb5e8c9e9baef4ce90c00efcfe7baef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1901",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……汉肯中佐！",
   "zh_hex": "150909ef82e93def4eefbaef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x192c",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "明白！阿伽玛、转入迎击态势！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef39e809ef97e7d2e8e8e84502e9c2e891e931e7cce994e8fdef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x195f",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "托雷斯！立刻联络先锋母舰的贝拉舰长{00}！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f4e8afe7c806e86be91fef2eeb14b8e967e9d5e7d4e7b4e857e7c2e7d4ef34000600000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1974",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "提坦斯来袭！通知他们转入迎击态势！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e821e843e7c8efcfe9aeef97ef59e85ae80ce7bbe9c2e891e931e7cce994e8fdef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x19b0",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……明白！！",
   "zh_hex": "150909ef39e80906060000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x19f7",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "呜、呜呜……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8d902e8d9e8d909090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a65",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "真能用吗？那个福·村雨？",
   "zh_hex": "15e820e7c6d8e80205e7b7e828ea7c04eb8eebad050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a9c",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在月球之所以输给了奥古、原因就在于控{00}制还不够充分",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29e850efd3e7cde7fbe7f3e8b9e839e7bae82be84d02e8e4ef33e7c5ef29e879ea3f00e8dee7f7e7b5e920ea86efae0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1abc",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "所以、我们才像那样对她施加了精神控制{00}……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7fbe7f3028be7bbe836e8e9e7b7e7dae7bee88eeb8de854e7bae98de9aaea3fe8de000909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1aeb",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……不对",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b5e7be0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1af7",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "问题就在于、非得控制到那种地步、她才{00}派得上用场",
   "zh_hex": "15e997ea12e7c5ef29e87902e8f0e80aea3fe8dee7d7e7b7e7d1ef63ea9302e88ee83600e985e80aef4cefb3e8760000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b2f",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那、那是……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b702e7b7e7b609090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b54",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……算了吧",
   "zh_hex": "150909e889e7bae7d00000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b5f",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "反正手头的战力本来就有限、我也不会强{00}人所难",
   "zh_hex": "15e87cef3bef66e92ee7b4ef28efb0efa6efcfe7c5e7cbeb2302efcce7c0e7b5e7e2e8ad00efb2e7fbe8660000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b7d",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "怎么靠现有的战力来应付、本就是我的分{00}内事",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f2e7bde8c7e82fe7cbe7b4ef28efb0efcfe873e97e02efa6e7c5e7b6efcce7b4efae00e99aefb80000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1bef",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "小看你了",
   "zh_hex": "15e83ee7f6e7b8e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c15",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……是玛雅啊",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b6e845ebfde7c30000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c38",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "看来你也渐渐懂得、该怎么去带领一支部{00}队了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f6efcfe7b8e7c0ed83ed83e8b0e80a02e898e7f2e7bde7ebe937ea20efb6e883ef7000e7c9e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c6c",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……是吗？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b6e802050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c91",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "一直以来的你、总是凭着个人的情绪在行{00}动",
   "zh_hex": "15efb6e875e7f3efcfe7b4e7b802e881e7b6ea49e86de828efb2e7b4e88befeeef29efd600ef300000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ca8",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可那样下去、你别想往上爬、一辈子只能{00}当个小兵",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7b7e7daef4de7eb02e7b8e7e5e7e6e911ef4cee5d02efb6ed0ce886ef32e7c600ef53e828e83eef930000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ce4",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "被扎夫特和新吉翁这么一逼、如今的提坦{00}斯已是命悬一线",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f1e84be830e7cfe7d3ef8ae7d9ee88e7b9e7bd87ebf602e7f0a2e7b4e821e84300e7c8ef3ae7b6e853ec6c87e9160000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1cfe",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "一旦落到那种地步、就算再不情愿、也不{00}得不去学",
   "zh_hex": "15efb6ebcde92ae7d7e7b7e7d1ef63ea9302e7c5e889e80be7b5e88be96102e7c0e7b500e80ae7b5e7ebeb550000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d1b",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……再说、西罗克还特意给我派了个监视{00}的人",
   "zh_hex": "150909e80be7ed02e7f8e7ece7d5e7f7e7cfef3ce839efcce985e7bae828ed8de9d900e7b4efb20000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d39",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可不能干出什么丢人现眼的事来",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7b5e7c6e8d3efbee7dde7bdebb0efb2e82fe90be7b4efb8efcf0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d62",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……她们",
   "zh_hex": "150909e88ee7bb000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d6c",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "竟把从奥古叛投过来的人派到我这儿、那{00}家伙……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2ce81be88ae82be84def43e948ef36efcfe7b4efb2e985e7d7efcce7b9eb7c02e7b700e7dfe7fd09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1da2",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "信赖是谈不上、不过能力倒是可以信得过",
   "zh_hex": "15e90feb46e7b6eaf4e7b5ef4c02e7b5ef36e7c6efb0e848e7b6e7c4e7f3e90fe80aef360000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1db9",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "只要在这里击落阿伽玛、就能把战力集中{00}到扎夫特和新吉翁身上",
   "zh_hex": "15ef32ef2aef29e7b9ef31e7cce92ae7d2e8e8e84502e7c5e7c6e81bef28daea98c000e7d7e84be830e7cfe7d3ef8ae7d9ee88e88db20000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1dd9",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "只要是为了这个、不管什么东西、我都会{00}拿来当战力使",
   "zh_hex": "15ef32ef2ae7b6e7c1e7bae7b9e82802e7b5e93be7dde7bde8bae7f802efcce840e7e200e9a7efcfef53ef28efb0e83f0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e53",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b809090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e5a",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你要记住哦、在你身后、永远都有我{00}在……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8ef2ae996e859e91902ef29e7b8e88de7fe02e9bfe94ce840e7cb8b00ef290909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1eb1",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……主人、出击的时间就快到了",
   "zh_hex": "150909e954efb202efbee7cce7b4ef2de8fce7c5e85fe7d7e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1edf",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊、是瑟拉啊、已经到那个时间了吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c302e7b6e8aae7c2e7c302ef3ae8b7e7d7e7b7e828ef2de8fce7bae802050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f0b",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "捷利特队准备出击",
   "zh_hex": "15e7bce82ee7cfe7c9e87ae877afe7cc000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f1e",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "捷利特队先行开路",
   "zh_hex": "15e7bce82ee7cfe7c9b89fe7fae8d20000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f2f",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "接着、再由我们从后方袭击阿伽玛、这就{00}是这次的作战计划",
   "zh_hex": "15efcee86d02e80be8a6efcce7bbe88ae7feefb1e9aee7cce7d2e8e8e84502e7b9e7c500e7b6e7b9e864e7b4ef2fef28ea55ea740000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f6d",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……不、瑟拉、你留在后方待命",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b502e8aae7c202e7b8e98cef29e7feefb1eaa8e8530000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f9b",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……主人？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e954efb2050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1fbe",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这一战不动用塞壬、改乘法夫尼尔出击",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9efb6ef28e7b5ef30efb3e950ec5902e9f0ebb1e84ee830e896e7e1efbee7cc0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ff0",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那……只要是主人您所期望的",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b70909ef32ef2ae7b6e954efb2e835e7fbeac9e965e7b40000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x201b",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这一回、我也要全力以赴",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9efb6ef5202efcce7c0ef2aefb4efb0e7f3eb1c0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2029",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "法夫尼尔的负荷、说不定会把你的大脑彻{00}底烧坏哦？",
   "zh_hex": "15e84ee830e896e7e1e7b4e92cedb102e7ede7b5e867e7e2e81be7b8e7b4efa5eb67ebc500e9b4ec29e9ede919050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2061",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "只要能帮得上主人的忙……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef32ef2ae7c6e910e80aef4ce954efb2e7b4ea0609090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x208c",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、就算要因此杀掉西格、你也愿意？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02e7c5e889ef2aef33e7cae89be9d3e7f8e82402e7b8e7c0e961ef3c050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x20bb",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……只要是主人所愿……",
   "zh_hex": "150909ef32ef2ae7b6e954efb2e7fbe96109090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x20e5",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "呵呵、回答得真好啊、瑟拉",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3def3d02ef52ea96e80ae820e7c7e7c302e8aae7c20000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x20f4",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哪怕你早已被设计成、只能以那种方式去{00}回答……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8ffe958e7b8e963ef3ae7f1eb43ea55e83702ef32e7c6e7f3e7b7e7d1efb1ea26e7eb00ef52ea9609090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5a4e",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……怎么样、梅丽贝尔？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7f2e7bde7da02e9f2e9c5e857e7e1050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5a7b",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "感觉好极了哦、基姆！",
   "zh_hex": "15e87de8aee7c7eacae7bae91902e829e823ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5aae",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "∀吗……作为一份见面礼、这可阔气得过{00}头了",
   "zh_hex": "15effee8020909ef2fe7c1efb6ea22e85ce862eb6502e7b9e7c4eec0e8ede80aef3600e92ee7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5ae6",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可尽管如此、金卡拉姆阁下您看上去却不{00}怎么高兴啊？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e8f2e93be7f0e7ca02e902e801e7c2e823e8d7ef4de835e7f6ef4ce7ebeadfe7b500e7f2e7bde812eabae7c3050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5b21",
   "jp_len": 39,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "一仗都没打、就把敌方最重要的一张底牌{00}弄到了手、自然觉得扫兴",
   "zh_hex": "15efb6ea37e840e7d8e7f502e7c5e81be7e3efb1e8c5e8a1ef2ae7b4efb6eac5e9b4ec2b00eac4e7d7e7baef6602efb5e7efe8aee80aeb88eaba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5b63",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这就是政治、阁下",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7c5e7b6ea68ea7902e8d7ef4d0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5b90",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……哼",
   "zh_hex": "150909e8b30000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5bb2",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "请恕我直言",
   "zh_hex": "15e83aeb04efcce875efd70000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5bc0",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "金卡拉姆舰队虽说具备了充足的战力、不{00}过……",
   "zh_hex": "15e902e801e7c2e823e7d4e7c9e8b8e7edea14e877e7baea86ea1ee7b4ef28efb002e7b500ef3609090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5bd8",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可在这类方面、似乎就有些考虑不够周到{00}了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4ef29e7b9e841efb1e86202e944e933e7c5e7cbe8a4eb41eba1e7b5e920ea5ce7d700e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5c14",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你是说、要替我们补上欠缺的政治手腕？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7b6e7ed02ef2aea50efcce7bbea81ef4cee44ee81e7b4ea68ea79ef66ee8e050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5c43",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我愿尽上一份微薄之力、为金卡拉姆阁下{00}的霸业效力",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce961e8f2ef4cefb6ea22eb58ee97e7cdefb002e7c1e902e801e7c2e823e8d7ef4d00e7b4eefdeadaea8fefb00000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5c7c",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "好个小小谋士……！是想把本将也一并拉{00}拢过去吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c7e828e83ee83eea6eef640909ef97e7b6e7e6e81befa6e84ae7c0efb6e957e7c200ed65ef36e7ebe802050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5caf",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那点小把戏对您行不通、这我也心里有数",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e822e83ee81bea3ee7bee835efd6e7b5ef5902e7b9efcce7c0e82def31e7cbe9140000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5ccd",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我只是想借阁下之手、来建立起我所坚信{00}的理想……",
   "zh_hex": "15efccef32e7b6e7e6eadce8d7ef4de7cdef6602efcfea61e86be847efcce7fbeb80e90f00e7b4e872e7e609090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5cec",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这便是我毫不掩饰的真心话",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e8fae7b6efccea0ae7b5ec72eec8e7b4e820e82de81f0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5d1e",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……哼、也好、就先拿你来利用一番吧",
   "zh_hex": "150909e8b302e7c0e7c702e7c5b8e9a7e7b8d9e82ed887ee6de7d0000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5d52",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "多谢阁下",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e9e8b2e8d7ef4d0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5d76",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "梅丽贝尔！热身也差不多该结束了！",
   "zh_hex": "15e9f2e9c5e857e7e1ef97ead1e88de7c0e9c7e7b5e7e9e898e868e895e7baef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5d88",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "如今∀与倒X这两台机体都已到手、该是{00}行动的时候了……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f0efb9effee832e848eed9e7b9e97dea16e7e4ef4fe840ef3ae7d7ef6602e898e7b600efd6ef30e7b4ef2dea39e7ba09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5de3",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "御大将！！",
   "zh_hex": "15ec68efa5e84aef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5e08",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "怎么了？是那帮叫奥古的追上来了吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f2e7bde7ba05e7b6e7b7e910e8c1e82be84de7b4e8ddef4cefcfe7bae802050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5e37",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不、不是！来的不是奥古！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b502e7b5e7b6ef97efcfe7b4e7b5e7b6e82be84def97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5e4b",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "一艘战舰、外加若干台MS！！",
   "zh_hex": "15efb6eb18ef28e7d402e8f7e854e7e7e8d3ea16efa7ef9eef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5e5a",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "对方、是宇宙海盗！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7beefb102e7b6e8bee8bfe91be9f3ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5e8e",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "夺取∀高达！！X1立即出击！",
   "zh_hex": "15ea17e987effee812ef2bef97ef97eed9eff7e86be855efbee7ccef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5f02",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那就是那台叫∀的高达吗……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7c5e7b6e7b7ea16e8c1effee7b4e812ef2be80209090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5f3e",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……好！金凯度·纳乌、这就出击！！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7c7ef97e902e95fe96def4be882e94d02e7b9e7c5efbee7ccef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5f83",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "呵呵……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3def3d09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5faf",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "扎比涅！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e84be825eacf0605000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x5fe8",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "光凭你一个人、怕是会忙不过来吧？",
   "zh_hex": "15e83dea49e7b8efb6e828efb202e958e7b6e7e2ea06e7b5ef36efcfe7d0050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x601d",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……啧、随你的便吧！！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e9fa02e9a1e7b8e7b4e8fae7d0ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x605e",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "呵呵、哈哈哈……！那是当然、我就不客{00}气地接受了！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3def3d02e7e8e7e8e7e80909ef97e7b7e7b6ef53e7ef02efcce7c5e7b5eccb00e8edef63efcee8c8e7baef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x60ab",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "（这可不行啊……怎能让贝拉大人在这种{00}地方栽跟头！）",
   "zh_hex": "150ae7b9e7c4e7b59fe7c30909e7f2e7c6e7f9e857e7c2beb4ef29e7b9e7d100bfd0ec5de973e92e060b00000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x60f2",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "御、御大将！！",
   "zh_hex": "15ec6802ec68efa5e84aef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6118",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "磨磨蹭蹭地干什么！既是敌人、就给我快{00}准备开战！！",
   "zh_hex": "15ec81ec81ec98ec98ef63e8d3e7dde7bdef97e8c4e7b6e7e3efb202e7c5e839efcce85f00e87ae877e7faef28ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6154",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可、可是、对付海盗的作战模拟、我们还{00}没做过啊……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c402e7c4e7b602e7bee97ee91be9f3e7b4ef2fef28ea91ebc902efcce7bbe7f700e7d8e81cef36e7c309090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6183",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "什么都照着手册一板一眼地办、那是蠢货{00}才会干的事！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dde7bde840ea1ae86def66ede2efb6ed75efb6e90bef63e8ea02e7b7e7b6e94beaf500e836e7e2e8d3e7b4efb8ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x61a0",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "还不快把MS都给我派出去！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f7e7b5e85fe81befa7ef9ee840e839efcce985efbee7ebef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x61d6",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "少爷……",
   "zh_hex": "15efaced8509090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x61f8",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "当着基姆·金卡拉姆的面、我们也有必要{00}展露一下实力",
   "zh_hex": "15ef53e86de829e823ef4be902e801e7c2e823e7b4e86202efcce7bbe7c0e7cbe860ef2a00e989e858efb6ef4de87fefb00000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6214",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我们也前进！威尔盖姆、准备进行对MS{00}战！",
   "zh_hex": "158be7bbe7c0bae89206e96be7e1ec7ee82302e87ae877e8929fe7be131400ef2806000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x624e",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "冲过来了吗……那也好",
   "zh_hex": "15e95eef36efcfe7bae8020909e7b7e7c0e7c70000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x625f",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那就让我亲眼见识见识、传闻中那些未来{00}人的战力！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7c5e7f9efcce894e90be85ce92fe85ce92f02ea38ebacef4ee7b7e8a4e8b4efcf00efb2e7b4ef28efb0ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x62aa",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……扎比涅！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e84be825eacf06000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x62b2",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "瞄准那台叫∀的MS的动力部、一举打得{00}它动弹不得！",
   "zh_hex": "15ea30e87ae7b7ea16e8c1effee7b4efa7ef9ee7b4ef30efb0ef7002efb6ea21e7f5e80a00e978ef30e946e7b5e80aef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x62f3",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……明白",
   "zh_hex": "150909ef39e8090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6322",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "好……上！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c70909ef4cef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6352",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "夺取∀高达！！X1、X2立即出击！",
   "zh_hex": "15ea17e987effee812ef2bef97ef97eed9eff702eed9ef5fe86be855efbee7ccef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x63b0",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……唔？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e81d050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x63de",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "咦？萨、扎比涅先生？",
   "zh_hex": "15ef4905e83b02e84be825eacfb8b60500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x640c",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……这不是金凯度！？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b9e7b5e7b6e902e95fe96def97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x643e",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……我在这里",
   "zh_hex": "150909efccef29e7b9ef310000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x647a",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "金凯度！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e902e95fe96def97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x64a6",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "很不巧、我对你这家伙、可没那么信得过",
   "zh_hex": "15e981e7b5ec1302efcce7bee7b8e7b9e7dfe7fd02e7c4e7d8e7b7e7bde90fe80aef360000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x64c1",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "贝拉的护卫、就由我来负责",
   "zh_hex": "15e857e7c2e7b4e8e0e9b202e7c5e8a6efccefcfe92ceba60000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6532",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……托比亚！那个长胡子的、就是我们的{00}目标！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7f4e825e7d606e7b7e828ef34ec8be886e7b402e7c5e7b68be7bbe7b400d5e96f06000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6546",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "用X3一击废掉它的动力部……办得到吧{00}！？",
   "zh_hex": "15efb3eed9ef60efb6e7cceae5e9d3e978e7b4ef30efb0ef700909e8eae80ae7d7e7d000ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x658a",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……是！我会想办法试试看！！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b6ef97efcce7e2e7e6e8eae84ee91de91de7f6ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x65c6",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊啊！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c3e7c3ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x65fe",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不好了！……贝拉！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5e7c7e7baef970909e857e7c2ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x663e",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那是什么东西！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b6e7dde7bde8bae7f8ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6680",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可恶、是月光蝶吗！这帮可恨的海盗！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7de02e7b6e850e83dea03e802ef97e7b9e910e7c4e9bee7b4e91be9f3ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x66be",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "绝不能让威尔盖姆沉没！米哈埃尔大佐、{00}快后退！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e91ce7b5e7c6e7f9e96be7e1ec7ee823e983e7d806e878e7e8e96ae7e1bea30200e85fe7fee88006060000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x670a",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这家伙！到底想干什么啊！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7dfe7fdef97e7d7e9b4e7e6e8d3e7dde7bde7c3ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6742",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "就是现在！快回收∀！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c5e7b6e82fef29ef97e85fef52e926effeef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x677a",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可恶！下次再让我碰上你、绝不轻饶！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7deef97ef4de864e80be7f9efcceb98ef4ce7b802e91ce7b5e990eab5ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x67ba",
   "jp_len": 38,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "区区一两只海盗罢了！！正好拿来给∀热{00}身、是个不错的对手！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef35ef35efb6e97def32e91be9f3eaefe7baef97ef97ef3be7c7e9a7efcfe839effeead100e88d02e7b6e828e7b5e885e7b4e7beef66ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6801",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "光是仗着机体的性能、可休想打倒我这个{00}金凯度！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e83de7b6ea37e86de7e4ef4fe7b4e951e7c602e7c4e90ee7e6e7f5e848efcce7b9e82800e902e95fe96def97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6846",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "呵、呵呵……哈哈哈……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3d02ef3def3d0909e7e8e7e8e7e809090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6853",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这都是为了贝拉大人……那台MS、我就{00}收下了、女人！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e840e7b6e7c1e7bae857e7c2efa5efb20909e7b7ea16efa7ef9e02efcce7c500e926ef4de7ba02efadefb2ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6890",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这、这家伙……！？真是个叫人发毛的对{00}手！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b902e7b9e7dfe7fd0909ef9705e820e7b6e828e8c1efb2e870eb60e7b4e7be00ef66ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x68d2",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "瞄准动力部、一击就封住它的行动……",
   "zh_hex": "15ea30e87aef30efb0ef7002efb6e7cce7c5eb83e859e978e7b4efd6ef3009090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x68e9",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "上啊、托比亚！！",
   "zh_hex": "15b2e7c302e7f4e825e7d606060000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6916",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "同样是高达、我这台可不一样！臭小子给{00}我滚一边去！",
   "zh_hex": "15e85de7dae7b6e812ef2b02efcce7b9ea16e7c4e7b5efb6e7daef97ecfde83ee886e83900efccece8efb6e899e7ebef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x695a",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "高达上竟画着骷髅标记、真是大胆包天啊{00}！",
   "zh_hex": "15e812ef2bef4cef2cecefe86dedcdedcfe96fe99602e820e7b6efa5edaeeabbe844e7c300ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6974",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "要不要就这么把你压扁、碾成肉泥啊……{00}！？",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2ae7b5ef2ae7c5e7b9e7bde81be7b8e992ee2802ed95e837edabed7fe7c3090900ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x69b7",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "比起月之民、那家伙的作风、反倒更像我{00}们这边的……",
   "zh_hex": "15e825e847e850e7cdef3802e7b7e7dfe7fde7b4ef2feb7502e87ce848e952e8e98b00e7bbe7b9e899e7b40909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x69f6",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可恶！区区海盗之流！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7de06ef35ef35e91be9f3e7cdea2e06060000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6a2e",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那就是敌方的主将吗……动手吧、扎比涅{00}！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7c5e7b6e7e3d0e7b4e954e84ae8020909ef30aee7d002e84be825eacf000606000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6aae",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d0909ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6ade",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那就是敌方的首领吗",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7c5e7b6e7e3efb1e7b4ef40ea20e8020000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6b19",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……扎比涅先生！？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e84be825eacfb8b606050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6b4a",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哈哈、有趣！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e8e7e802e7cbea8206060000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6b58",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "除了那帮叫奥古的家伙、没想到竟还有这{00}等高手！",
   "zh_hex": "15e974e7bae7b7e910e8c1e82be84de7b4e7dfe7fd02e7d8e7e6e7d7ef2ce7f7e7cbe7b900e826e812ef66ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6ba3",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "看样子、那家伙就是你们的王牌了吧、不{00}过……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f6e7dae88602e7b7e7dfe7fde7c5e7b6e7b8e7bbe7b4e884ec2be7bae7d002e7b500ef3609090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6be9",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在此就分出胜负、未免太可惜了",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29e7cae7c5efaeefbee8dbe92c02e8b4eb7de86ae7c4e9c8e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6bfa",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "反正你们也打算去投靠那个叫奥古的吧？",
   "zh_hex": "15e87cef3be7b8e7bbe7c0e7f5e889e7ebe948e8c7e7b7e828e8c1e82be84de7b4e7d0050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6c17",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那这场胜负、就留到那时再分吧！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b9e876e8dbe92c02e7c5e98ce7d7e7b7ef2de80bcde7d00600000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6c44",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "金卡拉姆阁下！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e902e801e7c2e823e8d7ef4def97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6c68",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "以多围少的这种打法、对身为武人的我来{00}说、实在有违本意！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f3e7e9e9deeface7b4e7b9e7d1e7f5e84e02e7bee88de7c1e8ecefb2e7b4efccefcf00e7ed02e87fef29e7cbeab2efa6ef3cef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6caa",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "金卡拉姆阁下！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e902e801e7c2e823e8d7ef4def97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6cda",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……他自己退走了吗",
   "zh_hex": "150909e80cefb5e8c9e880e890e7bae8020000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6ce6",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "要是真刀真枪地打起来、会是什么结果…{00}…想想都直冒冷汗",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2ae7b6e820ed25e820eaaebfe7f5e847d902e7e2e7b6e7dde7bde868e871090009e7e6e7e6e840e875eb7feb4eee4a00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6d2e",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b90909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6d5e",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是奥古的各位吧",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6e82be84de7b4e819e834e7d00000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6d69",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那台叫∀的机体、已经由我们替你们夺回{00}来了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7ea16e8c1effee7b4e7e4ef4f02ef3ae8b7e8a6efcce7bbea50e7b8e7bbea17ef5200efcfe7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6d9f",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你们究竟是……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7bbe906ef2ce7b609090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6dc9",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我们是十字先锋",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7bbe7b6ea4ae980ef8be9670000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6dd7",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……是宇宙海盗",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b6e8bee8bfe91be9f30000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8b52",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "冲上来了吗……有趣！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e95eef4cefcfe7bae8020909e7cbea82ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8b92",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……什么！！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7dde7bd06060000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8bd4",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "什么！！难道这就是……有质量的残像{00}！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dde7bd0606e866e82ae7b9e7c5e7b60909e7cbeb45e851e7b4e97be8e900060500000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8c1e",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……呵呵",
   "zh_hex": "150909ef3def3d0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8c56",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔！可恶！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e81def97e7c4e7deef97ef970000"
  },
  {
